## 5. Outline (Chỉnh sửa)

`age_anchor` + `physical_state` → chuyển sang **outline** (không ở phase plan):

```json
{
  "chapter_number": 7,
  "chapter_title": "Level 7: The Name",
  "chapter_type": "body",
  "level_number": 7,
  "age_anchor": "You are 44.",
  "physical_state": "Scarred, hardened, but physically peak",
  "main_key_data": ["200,000 people kneel, proclaimed Genghis Khan", 
                     "Sworn brother delivered in chains, asks noble death"],
  "sub_key_data": ["White banner raised nine times", "shaman say sky god chose you"],
  "opening_style": "callback",
  "chapter_structure": "action_scene",
  "closing_type": "paradox",
  "emotional_beat": "hollow_victory",
  "word_count_target": 180
}
```

**Mới:** `opening_style` field — outline AI chọn 1 trong 5 kiểu (standard, callback, thesis, atmosphere, cold_open) → writer dùng làm hướng dẫn.

